{"tid":271726,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"市區至少一連6日33°C或以上 幾時先落雨？","createTime":"2017-06-05T09:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T10:52:26.000Z","uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe6ba1436652b30a6de2af7f20d6b6081f5ff93","tid":271726,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"一股偏南氣流正為廣東沿岸帶來酷熱天氣，尖沙嘴天文台總部下午錄得33.5&deg;C，是今年以來最高紀錄，但熱辣辣的天氣仍要持續一段時間，因西北太平洋的副熱帶高壓脊會向西伸展，本港中後期將繼續天晴酷熱，天文台料市區氣溫至少一連5日高見33&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n雖然本港又熱又曬，惟天文台指，在副熱帶高壓脊西伸前，局部地區未來一兩日，仍有一兩陣驟雨，至周末起才再有驟雨。"},{"pid":"1d238aebf02768c74737d306b59be3c9bd55c585","tid":271726,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170605/large/1496655582_2c41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170605%2Flarge%2F1496655582_2c41.jpg&h=51bb8a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱死寶寶了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9addecab43c02dd363d5746279df1b83762cbf5e","tid":271726,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d816b88b0536fac1763dadacef0cf17f4dc6e38","tid":271726,"uid":42402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"濕熱嚟講 香港真係世界第一"},{"pid":"6ae228593cc0da2e3829926078a5aa56d27e8231","tid":271726,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"長期陰天 焗到仆街"}]}